The late warriors started to focus on the threat of that small whirlwind of a boy.

No longer were there any distinctions between Imperial soldiers and rebels, but everyone's consciousness was united in stopping that boy. That was, in a sense, the scene of a great achievement, stopping a civil war all alone.

However, their decision to be brave was not followed by a peaceful answer.

Lean back and avoid the blade. Dance back and avoid fist strikes. Go between the legs and avoid axe blows. Dodge arrows, dodge spears, dodge fangs, dodge shields, dodge, dodge, dodge, dodge, dodge, dodge, dodge, dodge, dodge, dodge, dodge, dodge, dodge, dodge - dodge, dodge, dodge, dodge.

