The boy's smile grew deeper as he boasted, effortlessly dodging the killing intent and hostility being hurled at him. The unfamiliar words uttered by the boy's mouth filled the warriors with a sense of unexplainable fear.

They should all have come to risk their lives in the battle to decide the course of this empire.

Nevertheless, they did not know the affiliation of the boy toying with them, the limit to his strength, the true meaning of his words and deeds, or anything.

I don't know what's going on, but everything seems to be going the way the boy wants it to――.

