The sensation of the sky, the ground, and the world shaking was felt by everyone on the battlefield at the moment.

Among those who could not treat it as anything else were those on the western ramparts who were to collide head-on with the flag-bearing groups running down the hillside―― the Imperial Soldiers ordered to defend the fourth bastion, which was closest to them.

